sources.name: Gapminder (Fertility v6)
sources.description:
Data published by Gapminder
Data publisher's source The data set was authored by  Ferenc Ajus and edited by Mattias Lindgren. The long list of original data sources is presented in the documentation.
Linkhttp://www.gapminder.org/documentation/documentation/gapdoc008_v2.pdf
Retrieved3 May 2016

Additional information

This is version 6 that was updated by Gapminder in January 2015.

Projections are mostly from the UN's World Population Prospects: The 2012 Revision.
